"href=\"ctx['iCal_url']\" target=\"_blank\" "
"class=\"planning_mail_template_button\">Add to iCal/Outlook</a>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <p t-if=\"ctx.get('open_shift_available')\">If you are "
"interested and available, please assign yourself this open shift.</p>\n"
"                    <p t-else=\"\">In case the current shift doesn't suit "
"you, we encourage you to reach out to your colleagues and request to switch "
"shifts. They might be interested in exchanging shifts with you.</p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
